23 (b) Serious impairment to bodily functions; or
24 (c) Serious dysfunction of a bodily organ or part.
25 (11) Requests for expedited external review, shall be forwarded by the insurer to the
26 independent review entity within twenty-four (24) hours of receipt by the insurer.
27 (12) For expedited external review, a determination shall be made by the independent
